INSTALL
--------------
For the impatient:
#python setup.py install
do:
 #fuglu --lint
 edit config files / install missing modules
while (you see errors in the output)
add a content filter to postfix config on tcp port 10025
run fuglu

For the a little more patient:
https://sourceforge.net/apps/trac/fuglu/wiki/FugluInstall

UPGRADE
--------
#python compareconfig.py
=> update your config accordingly
#python setup.py install
#fuglu --lint
restart fuglu

https://sourceforge.net/apps/trac/fuglu/wiki/FugluUprade